  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ドラゴンクエスト第2弾。ローレシアの王子たちがハーゴンを倒す冒険RPG。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Dragon Warrior II is an early top-down RPG that expands and improves on its predecessor. Unlike the first game, Dragon Warrior II allows the player to join forces with two other characters, a magic-using princess and a wizard-warrior prince.\n\nAlso including expanded monster battles involving up to 6 creatures and a much larger world, Dragon Warrior II is an important step in the evolution of the Dragon Warrior series.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Taking the role of a descendant of Erdrick, the player once again ventures forth in an effort to save the world.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
